ceName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb11740">Hofmannsthal, Hugo von</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02026">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, [10.? 9. 1911]</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L02028">Burckhard an Schnitzler, 12. 9. 1911</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02024">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, [26. 6. 1911]</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L02031">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 23. [9. 1911]</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
